description:
A libre server and cloud storage browser for Mac and Windows with support for FTP, SFTP, WebDAV, Amazon S3, OpenStack Swift, Backblaze B2, Microsoft Azure & OneDrive, Google Drive and Dropbox.


- [Bugfix] Invalid progress in Finder transferring multiple files (macOS) (#16738)
- [Bugfix] Diasble lookup of vaults by default. Must explicitly specify --vault (Cyptomator, CLI)
- [Bugfix] Duplicate file menu item always disabled (FTP) (#16798)
- [Bugfix] Allow OAuth configuration in connection profiles (WebDAV) (#16792)
